reviewText:
This is about a fifteen-minute video, which includes only one story, of how Rabbit tries to micromanage Pooh and friends in order to throw a party for his numerous rabbit relatives, at his (Rabbit's) house.  Tigger says he usually just invites people over for parties at his house and hopes for the best.

This episode is also available among the various episodes on Winnie the Pooh:  Pooh Party.

This Winnie the Pooh Vhs Contains 1 Original song And 1 Classic Episode

Song:
Happy Hundred Acre Wood Birthday

Episode:
Party Poohper
